data.description: Such a story to tell here. Formerly known as ''The Wayne Martin Farmhouse''', circa 1938,, a colonial revival that has made a journey & went through extensive renovations over the years all while maintaining the original charm. The lofted ceilings add to the already large floor plan. Offering 4 bedrooms, 1.5 ''spa vibes'' baths and an added shower in the lower level. Original hardwoods are refinished and sealed to preserve their authenticity. Interior has been freshly painted with a few other added personal touches. Enjoy your time in the open concept kitchen with wet bar then venture out to the screened in seasons room or in front of the gas fireplace. Large patio, deck, partial fenced in area with a tree lined back lot. Many species of plants/flowers will surely surprise you next spring
